Linux distros (+ Desktop environments)
This is a particular extremely versatile operating system and does not need any basic installation once you check "install third-party software". Great for personal use, not recommended for corporate use at desktop level, but unbeatable at the server level thanks to its fluidity, stability and above all security has no rival in the field of web servers, extremely discouraged with regard to its biggest flaw: "Its very limited software park and the unofficial support of the Drivers " Note: if your linux system has network problems, use the DNS servers and the modified local IP address.
